        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName>[Down]</placeName>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
<p>I am of opinion that M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. Horner’s Account of the researches made in the alluvial deposits of Ægypt, should be printed in the Philosophical Transactions,<ref target="#foot.f1"/> as the means of permanently recording valuable observations; and which observations probably will become in future times of still higher value.—</p>
<p>Charles Darwin <lb resp="#mjhawkins"/> Down  March 19<hi rend="superscript">th</hi>. 1855.</p>
<p>P.S. Figure 3 was not sent to me.</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
